&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Our &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.greenhouse.com/mission&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;mission&lt;/a&gt; at Greenhouse is to make hiring work for everyone – so we go to great lengths to hire great people because we believe that they’re the foundation of our success. At Greenhouse, you’ll join a team that collaborates purposefully, fosters inclusivity, and communicates with transparency and accountability so we can achieve our mission.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join us to do the best work of your career, solving meaningful problems with remarkable teams.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;Greenhouse is looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Customer Success Manager, Mid-Market&lt;/strong&gt; to join our team!&lt;/p&gt;
