&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Build and refine AI-powered workflows that reduce administrative work and scale how you deliver value across your book&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal bre

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Our &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.greenhouse.com/mission&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;mission&lt;/a&gt; at Greenhouse is to make hiring work for everyone – so we go to great lengths to hire great people because we believe that they’re the foundation of our success. At Greenhouse, you’ll join a team that collaborates purposefully, fosters inclusivity, and communicates with transparency and accountability so we can achieve our mission.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join us to do the best work of your career, solving meaningful problems with remarkable teams.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Greenhouse is looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Data Scientist&lt;/strong&gt; to join our team!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Data Scientist within our Corporate Development and Analytics department, you will join a multidisciplinary team of data scientists and business analysts dedicated to driving Greenhouse’s data strategy by building sophisticated data products. Serving as the bridge between raw product output and executive level decision making, you will partner upstream with Product teams to architect foundational telemetry, ensuring that every new feature is instrumented for deep dive analysis from day one. You will solve complex user pain points and ensure our long-term roadmap is backed by proactive, informed data productization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Who will love this job&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Connector &lt;/strong&gt;– You bridge the gap between complex statistical findings and actionable executive strategy to influence long-term roadmaps&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Technical Specialist &lt;/strong&gt;– You take pride in writing high quality, production ready code and applying engineering best practices to every data pipeline&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Cross-functional Partner &lt;/strong&gt;– You thrive when working alongside product and data platform teams to solve user pain points through shared expertise&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Data Strategist&lt;/strong&gt; – You prioritize a data-first approach, ensuring that telemetry and tracking are integrated into every stage of the product lifecycle&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;An Analyst &lt;/strong&gt;– You are energized by deep dives into data to uncover the core drivers of customer retention and product adoption&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Builder &lt;/strong&gt;– You enjoy creating scalable, automated analytical frameworks that replace manual tasks with long-term efficiency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;What you’ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate complex technical findings to executive leadership to influence Greenhouse&#39;s long-term roadmap&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Product Managers to identify opportunities where data science can solve user pain points&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct deep-dive statistical analysis to uncover the drivers of customer retention and product adoption&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, write, and maintain production-quality code (Python or SQL) to build scalable data pipelines, automated analyses, and predictive models&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write complex, highly optimized SQL queries to extract, clean, and transform large-scale datasets from cloud data warehouses (e.g., Snowflake, Redshift, or BigQuery)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Apply software engineering best practices to data science workflows, utilizing version control (Git), code reviews, and orchestration tools to ensure robust and reproducible analyses&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interface with distributed analysts to provide guidance on complex modeling and advanced statistical techniques&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advocate for data-first product design, ensuring that telemetry and event tracking are prioritized during the feature development lifecycle&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;You should

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Our &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.greenhouse.com/mission&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;mission&lt;/a&gt; at Greenhouse is to make hiring work for everyone – so we go to great lengths to hire great people because we believe that they’re the foundation of our success. At Greenhouse, you’ll join a team that collaborates purposefully, fosters inclusivity, and communicates with transparency and accountability so we can achieve our mission.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join us to do the best work of your career, solving meaningful problems with remarkable teams.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Greenhouse is looking for a &lt;strong&gt;GTM&amp;nbsp;Engineer&lt;/strong&gt; to join our Revenue Operations team!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;As the Revenue Intelligence Engineer, you’ll work closely with the Senior Manager, Revenue Operations to bridge the gap between engineering and business logic, translating real world requirements into deployed software that drives productivity across the entire Customer Growth &amp;amp; Success (CGS) lifecycle. You will play a foundational role in designing, building, and scaling our internal web applications used by multiple teams. This role is primarily responsible for designing, developing, engineering, deploying, and maintaining computer-based information systems and AI-enabled internal applications. Our initial build is a workflow automation and insights platform serving all GTM teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who will love this job&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Builder &lt;/strong&gt;- You thrive in a lean environment where you have high ownership, high velocity, and the technical discretion to choose what to build and how to build it using modern AI tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;An Internal Advisor&lt;/strong&gt; - You enjoy collaborating directly with revenue business leaders, using your technical acumen to patiently cut through ambiguous requirements and lead with confident product recommendations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Problem Solver &lt;/strong&gt;- You are motivated by challenges and love finding the right solution for your team, shipping custom features that immediately solve user friction&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;An AI Enthusiast&lt;/strong&gt; - You have a passion for AI assisted development, using tools like Claude Code to build useful tools for your team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, build, and extend new product features for our internal web app utilizing a modern tech stack composed of Next.js, TypeScript, Supabase, and Vercel&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build, test, and maintain robust, production grade data pipelines and automated integrations between core revenue engines like Salesforce and Gong&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner directly with Customer Growth &amp;amp; Success (CGS) stakeholders across SDR, AE, AM, and CSM teams to translate their daily business pain points into an actionable engineering roadmap&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluate, refine, and operationalize LLM prompts, open source AI frameworks, and third-party tools to optimize the validity and actionability of output data&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Document foundational technical architecture decisions and write clear operational playbooks so that your standalone systems can be easily maintained by the broader team over time&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate periodically with data engineering, security, and the Enterprise Apps team to ensure internal tooling integrates seamlessly with global corporate infrastructure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You should have&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years of direct experience working in a dedicated Revenue Engineering role or a highly technical Revenue Operations capacity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated experience using AI tools to build and extend app

