&lt;li&gt;An &lt;strong&gt;AI adopter and advocate&lt;/strong&gt; – You’re using the latest technologies to automate workflows, save time, and spend the creative human needed energy where it matters most.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
