&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Our &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.greenhouse.com/mission&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;mission&lt;/a&gt; at Greenhouse is to make hiring work for everyone – so we go to great lengths to hire great people because we believe that they’re the foundation of our success. At Greenhouse, you’ll join a team that collaborates purposefully, fosters inclusivity, and communicates with transparency and accountability so we can achieve our mission.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join us to do the best work of your career, solving meaningful problems with remarkable teams.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;This is an independent contractor engagement in Argentina. Deel will serve as Contractor of Record and will contract with and pay the independent contractor. The independent contractor will provide services to Greenhouse on a non-exclusive basis, may provide services to other clients, and will be responsible for determining the manner and means of performing the services, subject to the applicable statement of work and agreed deliverables. This engagement is not an employment relationship with Greenhouse. No employment relationship, social benefits, or labor entitlements under Argentine Law 20,744 are created by this engagement.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Through this arrangement, Deel is hiring an independent contractor to provide services to the Enterprise Apps team at Greenhouse.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;EA&#39;s charter is to take toil off every other team in the company so they can focus on the work only they can do. In 2026, we&#39;re using that charter to build something more ambitious: an AI-native operating layer for Greenhouse, with internal tooling, agents, skills, and automations that any team can build on, deploy to, and run against Greenhouse&#39;s data and tools. We&#39;re early enough in the work that the team will help shape what the platform actually becomes.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;You&#39;ll partner with leaders across Talent Acquisition, Customer Success, Marketing, Solutions, IT, and Finance to figure out which workflows are worth automating, then design and ship the solutions end-to-end with the rest of the team.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This role will support the development and maintenance of the Company’s web-based applications as part of an approximately 12-month engagement. In this role, you will focus on high-quality feature execution and technical reliability across the application stack for the Company&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This is a collaborative, execution-focused, non-exclusive engagement. Services will include building features, fixing bugs, and ensuring our products remain stable and performant for users.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
